data.description: If you are looking to downsize but aren't ready to give up all your space then this is the home for you.  It has 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths. Extra deep 1 car garage on the side of the house and another driveway at the front of the house. Huge living room on the main floor and large family room in the basement. Custom cabinets, big kitchen island. It comes with LG appliances including the Refrigerator. All LED Lighting and exterior lights. Large laundry room and spacious Pantry. Large main bedroom. Nice deck out back. Home is at Paint stage, should be finished in 30-45 days.
